    <h1>Interaction to Next Paint (INP)</h1>
    <p class="description">A Core Web Vitals metric measuring the time from a user interaction to the browser's next visual update. <strong>Good INP is under 200ms.</strong> Google replaced First Input Delay with INP in March 2024.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
